\f1\b PLACE
\f0\b0  and not pursue a 
\f1\b PERSON
\f0\b0 \cf2 \strokec2 \uc0\u8232 \
\pard\tx1660\tx2160\pardeftab720\li2160\fi-2160\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl2\cf2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u9642 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 If it\'92s about getting to a place then you just wait till you die to get there\uc0\u8232 \
\ls5\ilvl2\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u9642 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 If it\'92s about a person then you can pursue a relationship today and you are there.\uc0\u8232 \
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl1\cf2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u9702 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 The goal is to get more of Jesus\'85Jesus just happens to be in Heaven.\uc0\u8232 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
